{"type": "article", "id": 19413, "title": "LG 将首次亮相超级碗，要卖电视", "description": "曲面的OLED电视被导演Jake称作是，几乎是和Apple一样可以改变一切的科技。", "date": "2015-12-21T07:20:02Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 683, "name": "LG"}, {"id": 68, "name": "苹果"}, {"id": 14066, "name": "火星救援"}, {"id": 4361, "name": "超级碗"}, {"id": 64, "name": "广告"}], "category": 18, "author": 258307, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 33, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702101457ALHrC6aUBnPex8pG.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>这</span><span>周，</span><span>LG</span><span> 宣布他们将在明年 </span><span>2 </span><span>月 </span><span>7</span><span> 号的超级碗中推出 </span><span>60 </span><span>秒的</span><span> OLED </span><span>电视广告，这是 </span><span>LG</span><span> 第一次在美国最受关注的比赛上亮相。</span><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>而这个广告的导演将会是去年超级碗中拍出最受欢迎的</span><span> “Puppy Love”</span><span> 和</span><span> \r\n“Lost Dog”</span><span>的导演</span><span> Jake\r\nScott</span><span>。</span><span>Jake </span><span>的来头可不一般，他的父亲 </span><span>Ridley\r\nScott</span><span> 就是最近热映的《火星救援》的导演。</span><span>LG</span><span> 也表示 </span><span>Ridley </span><span>和他创立的 </span><span>RSA</span><span> 电影公司也可能会参与到 </span><span>LG</span><span> 的广告拍摄中。</span><span>LG</span><span> 最新的宣传海报中，</span><span>Jake</span><span> 和</span><span>Ridley</span><span> 也</span><span>都亮相了。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<iframe src=\"http://player.youku.com/embed/XMTQxOTAwMTI2MA==\" allowfullscreen=\"\" frameborder=\"0\">\r\n\t</iframe>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t去年超级晚上最受欢迎的广告之一《Puppy Love》\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<iframe src=\"http://player.youku.com/embed/XMTQxOTAwMTUxMg==\" allowfullscreen=\"\" frameborder=\"0\">\r\n\t</iframe>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t《Lost Dog》\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>除了《火星救援》外，</span><span>Ridley</span><span> 的成名作还包括了最经典的苹果《</span><span>1984</span><span>》广告，</span><span>但自那以后他就</span><span>没有接过超级碗的广告，媒体都在猜测这次和儿子</span><span>合作，</span><span> </span><span>Ridely</span><span> 会给 </span><span>LG </span><span>带来什么样的新创意</span><span>。</span><span> </span><span>总之 </span><span>LG</span><span> 对外宣传的是</span><span>“ </span><span>父亲和儿子结合了专业经验和创造力的合作</span><span>”</span><span>。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>“</span><span>当我第一次看</span><span> OLED</span><span> 电视时，它惊人的高清晰画面给我印象很深。</span><span>”\r\nRidely</span><span> 说。</span><span></span><span>儿子 </span><span>Jake </span><span>也</span><span>补充道，</span><span>“</span><span>《</span><span>1984</span><span>》让观众看到能改变一切的科技的进步，在 </span><span>LG </span><span>的</span><span> OLED</span><span> 电视上我看到了同样的可能。</span><span>” </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<iframe src=\"http://player.youku.com/embed/XMTQxOTAwMDkyNA==\" allowfullscreen=\"\" frameborder=\"0\">\r\n\t</iframe>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t著名的《1984》\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>根据《韩国商业新闻》的报道，今年 </span><span>LG</span><span> 又</span><span>新推出了五款 </span><span>OLED</span><span> 电视，目前在市面上销售的</span><span> OLED</span><span> 电视型号已经超过了 </span><span>10</span><span> 种。</span><span>LG</span><span> 是目前全世界最极力推广 </span><span>OLED</span><span> 技术的电视厂商，在韩国本土，已经超过了三星。</span><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>去年 </span><span>LG </span><span>发布了</span><span> OLED </span><span>电视</span><span> 55EC9300</span><span>，当时有媒体还将这款电视评价为</span><span>画质最好的电视</span><span>”</span><span>，</span><span>OLED</span><span> 屏幕的画质比</span><span> LED</span><span>、</span><span>LCD</span><span>（当前市面上最主流的屏幕技术）更好，不过它的价格高达</span><span> 3500</span><span> 美元（约合</span><span> 22207 </span><span>元人民币）。</span><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n"}